description:
"Death is not the end"
This piece is inspired by the song "Death is not the end" by Nick Cave, from his excellent album "Murder Ballads". The image came to me one day I listened to this song on my way to work. The motif stood before me clear as day.
The piece is also a small homage to one of my favourite artists, Edvard Munch. He was a master with lines. Both visible and invisible. 

For this piece I wont write any poem. I will just encourage you all to listen to the song, because those lyrics says it all.
